### MSME Agentic Operations - API Test File
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code
### Or use curl/Postman

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Input Gateway Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/status

###
### TEST 1: Website Order (Structured JSON)
###
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/website
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "customerId": "CUST-001",
  "customerName": "Rajesh Kumar",
  "productId": "PROD-123",
  "productName": "Widget A",
  "quantity": 15,
  "unit": "boxes",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "deadline": "2026-02-01T15:00:00Z",
  "notes": "Please pack carefully"
}

